dc_title_s: Plat book of the city of Saint Paul, Minn. and suburbs~~from official records, private plans and actual surveys
dc_creator_sm: St. Paul Real Estate Board (Saint Paul, Minn.); G.M. Hopkins & Co.
dc_description_s: Cartographic Details: Scale [1:200] and [1:100]. 200 ft. to the in. and 100 ft. to the in. Some maps presented at a scale of [1:300], 300 ft. to 1 in. Includes indexes. Dimensions: 1 atlas (124 unnumbered pages) : 58 colored maps ; 64 centimeters
